message.body: Thanks Bob, for this sweet welcome back text! I got swallowed up by the busy week. It's crazy how quickly clinic is approaching. I feel like I know nothing all of a sudden!! How are you holding up?
Oh pffffft. All that info is in there It will be at your fingertips when u need it.
I really don't know! My little sister just called me and said she thinks she has a hernia and I was like, what's that??!!!
Last time she called she thought she had parasites! lol
Haha. Sounds like She needs a sister w acupuncture needles HURRY!
She has already declared I will not needle her in the same way she would not try to be my social worker! It's probably just childhood torture from her older sister she's remembering.
I was pretty bad. It was mostly psychological torture though, so she shouldn't be afraid of a few little tiny needles!!
